data.text: Sophomore: Earned a berth on the varsity travel roster… Continued to gain experience on the JV squad… Freshman: Gained valuable experience playing for the Junior Varsity team… Secondary School Background: A graduate of Murrieta Valley High School where he lettered in football… Recipient of the Eric McMillan Legacy Award in football… Named the Defensive Back of the Year… All-League selection… Named a 2008 National Football Foundation Scholar-Athlete… Recipient of the Foreign Language award and Scholar-Athlete Award… Personal: William James Gray, born October 27, 1990… Son of Denise and Bill Gray… Enjoys guitar, chess, golf, and ping-pong… International Relations concentrator.
